cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.IR 

This paper involves the use of Generative Adversarial Networks (GANs) for generating high-resolution images of text with specific styles. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Additionally, the paper involves the use of text to image retrieval techniques, which falls under the category of cs.IR (Information Retrieval). The use of GANs also falls under the categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper involves the generation of license plates, which falls under the category of cs.GR (Graphics).
